<h1 class="title">SmoWeb</h1>
<div class="subtitle">The open computational platform by <a href="http://www.sysmoltd.com" target="_self">SysMo</a></div>
<div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">		
	<p>
		Welcome to our computational platform. Here you will find a
		number of one-page apps that could be used to tackle various
		engineering problems. Please select the appropriate page/app from
		the navigation bar on the top or choose one from the thumbnails below.
	</p>
	<p>
		We are currently at a major milestone: SmoWeb v. 1.0. To learn more about it,
		check our <a href = "/?model=Platform" target="_self">Platform</a> page. Here
		you will learn more about the platform in general,
		the current status and the development plans for the next release.
	</p>
	<p>
		We are actively searching for partners for our future development. If you 
		would like to collaborate with us, please <a href = "http://www.sysmoltd.com/?q=contact">contact us</a>. 
		We would also appreciate any kind of feedback or suggestions relevant to the platform
		and the application modules.
	</p>
	<p>
		We highly recommend that you use <span style="font-weight: bold;">Mozilla Firefox</span> or
		 <span style="font-weight: bold;">Google Chrome</span> to browse this website.
	</p>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">
{% for routerName, router in pageView.router.registry.iteritems() %}
	{% for pageName, viewClass in router.pages.iteritems() %}
		{% for module in viewClass.modules %}
			{% if issubclass(module, smo.model.model.NumericalModel) %}
				{% if module.showOnHome %}
					<a href="/{{routerName}}/{{viewClass.__name__}}?model={{module.__name__}}"
							 target="_self">
						<div class="thumb" 
							{% if hasattr(module, 'description') %}
								data-toggle="tooltip" title="{{module.description.asTooltip}}" tooltip
							{% endif %}>
							<div style="display: table-cell; vertical-align:middle; 
									height: 115px; width: 160px; margin-top: 10px;">
								<img {% if hasattr(module, 'figure') %}
										src="{{ static(module.figure.thumbSrc) }}"
									{% else %}
										style="opacity: 0.5; filter: alpha(opacity=50);"
										src="{{ static('img/ModuleImages/thumbnails/Calculator_thumb.png') }}"
									{% endif %}
								/>
							</div>
							<div style="display:inline-block; width: 150px; color: black;">
								{{module.label}}
							</div>
						</div>
					</a>
				{% endif %}	
			{% endif %}
		{% endfor %}
	{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
</div>
